<section id="TMBRole" class="section-padding-large">
    <div class="container text-black">
        <h3 class="mb-8">My Role</h3>
        <p class="h6 mb-8">I worked with the design team to rapidly prototype the new <span class="font-medium">Trusted Media Brands</span> website. The initial prototype was built in a static environment using <span class="font-medium">11ty</span>. When reviewed and approved internally, the static code was converted for use with the headless <span class="font-medium">Wordpress CMS + React</span> stack built by the back-end dev.</p>
        <p class="h6">Content intended on each template page was expected to be varied, and so much care was put into building an implementation of the design that accounted for existence, or lack-thereof, of content on each page.</p>
